# Title Director(s) Writer(s) Original air date Production code

17  "The Man Who Stole Tomorrow"  Sebastian Montes  Andrew Robinson  January 9, 2011  016
----:----------------------------:------------------:----------------:----------------:----

Kang the Conqueror comes from the 41st century to destroy Captain America, 
who Kang believes may soon cause his timeline to cease to exis.
The avengers try their best but are no match for Kang.
Kang then shows the avengers the destruction they are fighting for.
Finally Iron man gets control of Kangs chair he uses to teleport time.
He then teleports the team back to their own era.

 Introducing characters: Fantastic Four (Mister Fantastic, Invisible Woman, Human Torch, Thing)
